snippet.title: Silver The Hedgehog Worlds Collide launch trailer
snippet.description:
Here it is! The greatest Silver the Hedgehog Fan game EVA!!

Play as silver through 7 levels and Stop Eggman Nega from destroying Blaze and Silver's world from destruction using his latest invention, 'The Dimension Tunneller'.

Download it here
http://www.mediafire.com/file/pyn926al1ex1dhq/Silver_the_Hedgehog_-_Worlds_Collide.zip
